Package: DIVE
Type: Package
Title: Data Integration and Visual Exploration
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Anh Nguyet Vu
Maintainer: Anh Nguyet Vu <avu@coh.org>
Description: Utilities to integrate and visually explore a collection of partially connected datasets, e.g. datasets from different sources that contain distinct measurements for some or all of the same biological individuals. Creates a Shiny application that can provide different types of visual exploration/analysis for the mosaic data, and which incorporates ontology annotations or additional metadata for improved filtering and inference.
